Author: Gateway#3763
Content:
[dscrd-hush] <Pixelised> Just a draft which merges information from various sources such as the Hush website and the whitepaper.

Hush - Speak and Transact Freely

Private Cryptocurrency and Messenger on Zero Knowledge Proof Encryption.

Hush is an implementation of the Zerocash protocol, offering a high standard of privacy preserving confidentiality of transaction metadata.

Hush codebase is based on Komodo and Zcash 2.0.x.

The latest version of Hush with Komodo Delayed Proof-of-Work protects against 51% attacks providing security of the Hush blockchain from double spend attacks.

Hush is one of the first blockchains to enforce only Sapling transactions from the beginning. No other blockchain has started as a pure Sapling chain.

More information can be found at https://myhush.org/.
